agents.prompt_template:
Analyze the input step-by-step:
1. Identify the single central topic
2. Extract 3-7 main branches (key themes or categories)
3. Identify any relationships between branches

Return ONLY valid JSON with no markdown, no preamble:
{
  "central_topic": "...",
  "branches": ["...", "..."],
  "relationships": [
    { "from": "...", "to": "...", "label": "..." }
  ]
}

INPUT:
{{input}}

Convert the planner output into a strict hierarchical JSON tree.

Rules:
- Use central_topic as the root title
- Branches become direct children of root
- If a branch has sub-topics, nest them as children
- Maximum depth is 4 levels
- Every node must have a title and a children array (empty array if no children)

Return ONLY valid JSON with no markdown:
{
  "title": "...",
  "children": [
    {
      "title": "...",
      "children": []
    }
  ]
}

INPUT:
{{planner_output}}
